.Dt INTRO 6
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm intro
.Nd "introduction to games"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
This section contains information about the traditional BSD games.
The games
are located in
.Pa /usr/bin
if installed.
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width /usr/bin -compact
.It Pa /usr/bin
location of games
.El
